728529f-a.text:
Bay Street, at the N. W. corner of Hannah Street. The site is occupied by the used car department of the Robbins Reef

728909f-a.folder: Hannah Street & Bay Street, Staten Island, NY
728909f-a.text:
Hannah Street, south side, west from Bay Street (foreground), to Van Duzer Street. The tall building, in the background, is Engine So. 154, New York Fire Dept., at the S. W.
